title: Match of the Day - 21st March 2015 - hdtv x264

SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD   
Date: Saturday 21st March 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:55 

Gary Lineker is joined by Alan Shearer and Phil Neville for highlights from the day's eight Premier League matches, which include defending champions Manchester City v West Brom, Newcastle v Arsenal and West Ham v Sunderland. Tottenham host Leicester, Aston Villa play Swansea, Crystal Palace travel to Stoke, and Southampton welcome Burnley.
The studio experts are Alan Shearer and Phil Neville.
